Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is excited to offer 165 Robinsons Road, Ravenhall, for lease.

Key features on the property include;
+ Sizes ranging from: 866sqm* - 2,290sqm*
+ High clearance showrooms
+ Rear RSD access
+ Glass facade and multiple access doors
+ Surplus car parking for site
+ Male and female amenities
+ Lunch room
+ Cleaners store room

Location information: 
Directly facing Robinson's Road, which becomes Westwood Drive/Palmers Road is this development which will have access to the showrooms via Nexus Street, Orbis Drive and Barretta Road.

Robinsons Road is the main north south linkage and is located between the Princes Fwy/West Gate Fwy and the Western Fwy/Ballarat Road. Robinsons Road is soon to be upgraded which will increase the traffic volume passing by this development.

For further information or to arrange an on-site inspection, please contact the CBRE team. 

*approx.

CBRE is delighted to bring to market 9 Barretta Road, Ravenhall, for sale.

The property is currently tenanted by Agru Australia who commenced operation in 1990 and is a renowned supplier of high quality plastic products in the Australian market.

Over the past 30 + years, Agru has grown to be a major distributor of innovative plastic products including fittings, pipes, industrial piping systems, semi-finished products, concrete protection and liners.

Lease information:
+ Tenant: Agru Australia Pty Ltd
+ Term: Two (2) years
+ Rental: $95,692 pa net plus GST (from Sept 2021)
+ Commencement: 1st September 2020
+ Reviews: Fixed annual reviews of 3%
+ Options: Two (2) years  

Key highlights of the property include:
+ Land area: 1,748sqm*
+ High clearance warehouse
+ 8m wide crossover
+ 7m+ internal clearance
+ Fully fitted offices over two levels
+ Lunch room
+ Male and female amenities
+ Warehouse area of 852sqm*
+ Office over two levels of 241sqm*
+ Vendor terms - flexible financing available 
+ Dividing fence to be erected for new occupier
+ Existing permit for signage facing Robinsons Road

The property is located within the Orbis Business Park. The estate is strategically located at the intersection of Riding Boundary Road and Robinsons Road in Ravenhall, Melbourne's fastest growing industrial precinct, approximately 20km* west of the CBD. 

The estate is located within 1km* of the Robinsons Road exit/entry ramps to the Deer Park Bypass/Western Freeway and provides strong logistics links through to Melbourne's CBD and beyond. The northern suburbs are accessed 

The immediate surrounding area comprises a mix of commercial, industrial and residential uses along with a strong local workforce with supporting services.   

*approx.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: FREEHOLD INDUSTRIAL INVESTMENT IN PRIME WESTERN LOCATION

CBRE is delighted to offer, 8 & 10 Eucumbene Drive, Ravenhall, for lease. These two freestanding properties are separately titled and metred, and can be taken individually or together. 

Situated 200m* from the freeway entrance, these two office/warehouses will suit every occupier.

Ravenhall is experiencing significant growth in commercial and industrial activity, and is extremely well connected to Melbourne’s key infrastructure points:

LOCATION BENEFITS:
+ 13km* to Melbourne's Airport
+ 14km* to the Port of Melbourne
+ 18km* to Melbourne's CBD (Spencer St)
+ 13km* Melton

KEY FEATURES OF BOTH BUILDINGS:
+   High cubic capacity – 10m high internal clearance
+   Clear span warehouse – no columns
+   Large hard stand areas
+   High three phase power supply
+   Fully fitted offices and amenities
+   Two kitchenettes/tea rooms per property
+   Fully ducted heating/cooling
+   North facing
